      • getBilateralUtilUtilPlot

        public BooleanModel getBilateralUtilUtilPlot()
        Returns:
        A booleanModel containing a boolean. If true, a util-util graph instead of a default graph will be plotted. util-util graph is a graph with side A utilities on the X-axis and side B utilities on the Y axis. This visualization method allows us to also plot other points like the Pareto Frontier and Nash point.
